title: Golden Globes: Exclusive Backstage Photos of Leonardo DiCaprio, Paul Thomas Anderson, Jessie Buckley, Miley Cyrus and More Stars
summary: Photographer Guy Aroch hustled around The Beverly Hilton to capture the stars (Snoop Dogg! Emma Stone! Renate Reinsve!), the presenters (Adam Scott! Colman Domingo!) and, of course the winners (Teyana Taylor! Rose Byrne! 'Hamnet'! 'KPop Demon Hunters'!) on an epic Sunday.
